Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞之夜跟朋友的妈妈\N两个人独处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.40,0:01:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  老公吗\N你已经到达那边了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.41,0:01:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出差的地方出问题\N要两三天不能回来？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.09,0:01:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你知道今天是什么日子吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.26,0:01:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前不是说好了\N一家人一起过的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.10,0:01:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以说因为工作\N没有办法呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.10,0:01:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.44,0:01:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.28,0:01:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直无去相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.62,0:02:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聪   你今晚有什么打算呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.96,0:02:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚吗？\N听说爸爸今晚也不能回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.80,0:02:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗？\N今天是圣诞节吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.30,0:02:17.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以妈妈为了聪\N打算弄一餐丰富的晚餐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.81,0:02:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉，我要跟女朋友一起出去\N可是不会很晚的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.98,0:02:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道啦\N怎麽这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.32,0:02:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在已经不是一家人\N一起度过圣诞节的年龄了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.66,0:02:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个跟圣诞节没有关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.33,0:02:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有妈妈一个人在期待啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.16,0:02:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不要大过期待了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.17,0:02:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都大自私了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.53,0:03:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结婚之后，马上有了小孩的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.37,0:03:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是很一般的幸福家庭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.38,0:03:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们夫妻之间\N也被认为感情不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.71,0:03:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是随着小孩的成长\N越加的感觉到丈夫对我的不关心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.22,0:03:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每晚都会感觉到寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.93,0:04:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安_\N聪在吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.43,0:04:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真二君    他还没有回来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.77,0:04:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.77,0:04:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我改天再过来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.94,0:04:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等一下\N他应该很快就会回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.61,0:04:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你进来等他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.78,0:04:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是   今晚是圣诞节   家里只有阿姨\N一个人   你陪我起吃晚饭吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.96,0:04:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是\N你不用客气了进来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.13,0:04:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.32,0:05:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.82,0:05:16.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你多吃点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.49,0:05:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.16,0:05:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了    我们来干杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.19,0:05:59.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.36,0:06:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这个料理合你胃口就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.21,0:06:11.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们来干杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.04,0:06:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.54,0:06:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干杯   干杯\N谢谢你一直陪聪玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.22,0:06:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聪每天都很开心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.22,0:06:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你吃呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.89,0:06:33.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.90,0:06:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.90,0:06:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是跟我儿子上同所学校的真二君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.74,0:06:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是今年夏天    交友较少的儿子\N第一位带到家里来的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.77,0:07:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂\N你在干什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.44,0:07:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的房间在这呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.94,0:07:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了    你要喝什么吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.95,0:07:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀？    你是聪的朋友吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.29,0:07:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我同班同学真二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.13,0:07:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.29,0:07:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.47,0:07:52.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为工作关系   跟他爸两个人\N一起生活的他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.81,0:07:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之后     经常过来我家玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.48,0:08:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开始感觉    自己多了个儿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.32,0:08:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.74,0:09:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是聪吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.75,0:09:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候   我还没有察觉到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.42,0:09:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他看向我的眼神\N并不是看待朋友妈妈的眼神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.76,0:09:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且作为一位女性\N对我存在着意识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.44,0:10:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还很年轻\N可以吃很多的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.78,0:10:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甜的食物   也可以的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.28,0:10:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟小朋友打交道我也挺开心的\N可是无法交心呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.12,0:10:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.12,0:10:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我丈夫老是说工作工作的\N我也知道 工作很重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.96,0:10:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过过于心碌的话    就有点那个了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.97,0:10:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.14,0:10:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请吧你吃呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.48,0:10:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.99,0:10:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.32,0:10:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃呢\N好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.49,0:10:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了   真君你有女朋友了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.66,0:11:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在没有呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.33,0:11:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧？\N你有喜欢的对象吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.84,0:11:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.34,0:11:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是什么表情呀\N你在害羞吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.85,0:11:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.52,0:11:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个   我差不多\N你还不能走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.69,0:11:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要来玩游戏呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.53,0:11:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞节是狂欢节吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.58,0:12:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不行了\N我的屁股\N要碰到地面 了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.09,0:12:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的是蓝色的\N真的吗？不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.10,0:12:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  不行的   真二君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.60,0:12:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次看到你开始\N我就喜欢上你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.11,0:12:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真二君你是我儿子的朋友呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.28,0:12:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个没有关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.95,0:13:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会没有关系呢\N不行的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.12,0:13:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不我控制不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.12,0:13:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行    你停下来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.63,0:13:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁呢    这个时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.83,0:13:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我丈夫送的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.00,0:13:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不抽点时间出来    肯定是想着\N只要送花   就可以了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.67,0:13:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太差劲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.19,0:14:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂   阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.19,0:14:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.03,0:14:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.69,0:14:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.70,0:14:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.57,0:15:03.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨   不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.24,0:15:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你安静一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.26,0:15:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说无法忍耐吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.60,0:15:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以喔    我来让你爽快吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.60,0:15:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.45,0:15:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的     你就爽快吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.16,0:16:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不喜欢激烈一点的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.33,0:16:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是喜欢没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.67,0:16:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有奇怪的感觉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.12,0:18:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.99,0:19:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爽快吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.69,0:19:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.85,0:19:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨    我无法忍耐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.02,0:19:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行    不行   要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.86,0:19:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.05,0:20:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.11,0:21:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个\N对不起呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.62,0:21:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浴室的水放好了\N你去洗澡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.79,0:21:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去呀\N我借用一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.48,0:21:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于他的告白\N说实话  我很吃惊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.65,0:22:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是作为女性   我完全不觉得\N这是有错的   也是事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.66,0:22:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自对丈夫的不满与压力让我绷断了\N这根禁断的绳子自己踏入了这个禁区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.49,0:24:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个\N你绝对不要告诉任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.83,0:24:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你抱我呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:56.50,0:24:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你转过身子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:58.17,0:24:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我接吻呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:01.50,0:25:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:03.34,0:25:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是认真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:22.58,0:26:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个    我\N你是不是把我的内裤带走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:32.59,0:26:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你老实回答呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:35.76,0:26:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:39.43,0:26:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的内裤拿回去\N你打算干什麽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:45.94,0:26:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自慰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:49.95,0:26:51.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在也做吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:53.11,0:26:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:55.95,0:26:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:58.12,0:26:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:08.46,0:27:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用害羞的\N这样的事情你是第一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:15.64,0:27:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:48.17,0:27:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想不想摸胸部呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:54.34,0:27:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要怎么做呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:59.35,0:28:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把手给我呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:02.68,0:28:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用你的手掌    从下面开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:07.36,0:28:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样    慢点来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:14.20,0:28:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗？\N没错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:19.03,0:28:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:31.21,0:28:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你第一次摸胸部\N怎么样呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:34.72,0:28:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很柔软呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:37.55,0:28:39.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很柔软吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:40.89,0:28:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:43.73,0:28:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  按你喜欢的来动作吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:47.06,0:28:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:03.58,0:29:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里变硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:07.58,0:29:10.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能感觉到吗？\N是的  我能感觉到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:12.92,0:29:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的乳头\N变硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:18.93,0:29:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好淫荡呀\N淫荡是吗
