Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:54.46,0:29:58.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚刚才射了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:00.64,0:30:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过肉棒又变得适么精神了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:06.98,0:30:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为你对我做如此色情的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:10.48,0:30:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才会这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:13.65,0:30:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:22.32,0:30:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我接吻呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:47.02,0:30:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想射了\N不可以喔    还不能射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:54.02,0:30:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨来帮你吧
