Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:46.67,0:52:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:53.68,0:52:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真二君\N不行   要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:00.68,0:53:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:06.19,0:53:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么激烈的话\N阿姨会去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:11.03,0:53:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太爽快了\N所以没有控制住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:13.36,0:53:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你无法忍耐了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:18.03,0:53:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真二君    你因为爽快\N所以抽动了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:20.04,0:53:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:25.54,0:53:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穴好爽快阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:32.05,0:53:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:36.38,0:53:39.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你差点要射了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:41.22,0:53:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想我继续抽动吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:45.23,0:53:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想抽动\N你也想抽动吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:50.57,0:53:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以呀\N你过来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:00.91,0:54:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插入呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:03.91,0:54:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害   好湿呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:10.59,0:54:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨好湿了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:15.59,0:54:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨   我的抽动方式对吗？\N对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:37.28,0:54:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:41.62,0:54:43.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真二君你想这样抽动是吗\N是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:43.79,0:54:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太色情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:53.80,0:54:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的抽动方式\N太色情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:55.96,0:54:58.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽快阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:59.13,0:55:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨   好厉害\N越来越湿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:09.14,0:55:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽快呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:11.15,0:55:14.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以继续抽动吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:24.49,0:55:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以呀\N你按自己喜欢的方式来抽动吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:35.17,0:55:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:49.02,0:55:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:52.35,0:55:55.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨\N你怎么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:08.87,0:56:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:11.71,0:56:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经无法忍耐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:13.88,0:56:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以射到阿姨的里面吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:18.71,0:56:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我想在里面感受真二君的精夜\N可是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:26.39,0:56:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你射到外面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:30.73,0:56:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:32.23,0:56:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:40.90,0:56:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了\N射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:53.58,0:56:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真二君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:57.09,0:57:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又射了这么浓稠的精液出来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:03.26,0:57:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N你过来呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:07.93,0:57:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你舔干净吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:44.63,0:57:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他的恋爱   又新鲜又刺激就好像\N断了线一般   我们相爱着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:56.14,0:57:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是草莓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:58.81,0:57:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:03.99,0:58:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:07.66,0:58:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你吃草莓的样子   好漂亮\N你说什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:12.83,0:58:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要吃吗？\N我也要吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:16.33,0:58:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要奶油\N奶油是吗是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:20.84,0:58:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:23.00,0:58:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:27.68,0:58:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好色情    可是我吃不到吧\N可以吃到的   这里  怎么吃呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:34.68,0:58:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把舌头伸出来呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:43.19,0:58:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看呀   吃到了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:49.36,0:58:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃吧\N很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:52.87,0:58:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美味吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:55.54,0:58:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将舌头伸出来呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:04.05,0:59:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好甜呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:08.05,0:59:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:16.56,0:59:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美味的地方吗？\N美味的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:19.56,0:59:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:22.23,0:59:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不到乳头了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:23.90,0:59:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:24.07,0:59:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被藏住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:26.23,0:59:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看呀    在上面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:30.24,0:59:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不快点吃掉的话\N会融化的   要融化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:35.08,0:59:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:43.59,0:59:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扩散了\N扩散了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:02.27,1:00:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变干净了\N你的乳头挺立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:07.94,1:00:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会挺立啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:20.62,1:00:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比平常的还要美味\N比平常的遗要美味吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:24.96,1:00:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们继续来吃蛋糕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:33.13,1:00:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多蛋糕喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:39.31,1:00:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美味的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:41.98,1:00:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很美味喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:45.31,1:00:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要再吃一次吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:50.99,1:00:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你躺下来呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:56.49,1:00:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:58.83,1:01:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:02.00,1:01:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要喂我吗？\N我来喂你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:09.34,1:01:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把舌头伸出来呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:36.87,1:01:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睑上全部是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:41.20,1:01:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你睑上全部是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:55.05,1:01:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸部好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:57.55,1:01:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来接吻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:00.39,1:02:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗？\N可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:04.23,1:02:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你舔干净吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:18.41,1:02:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个脱掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:26.08,1:02:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好羞耻啊\N羞耻吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:29.42,1:02:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明变大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:41.43,1:02:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:44.43,1:02:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也帮我舔呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:20.80,1:03:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太美味了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:27.48,1:03:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你舔呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:32.31,1:03:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太美味了\N美味是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:55.67,1:03:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:02.84,1:04:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢胸部了\N你很喜欢胸部是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:14.19,1:04:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在晃动
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:16.86,1:04:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在晃动喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:19.03,1:04:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是惩罚
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:21.86,1:04:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惩罚你喜欢胸部
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:29.37,1:04:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你继续舔我的胸部\N我就要继续惩罚你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:37.38,1:04:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续惩罚吗？\N继续惩罚
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:41.05,1:04:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把腰部抬起来呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:43.22,1:04:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗？没错喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:46.72,1:04:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用胸部给你惩罚
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:53.06,1:04:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好硬呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:59.07,1:05:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很容易就硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:06.74,1:05:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:08.74,1:05:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内棒好热阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:14.25,1:05:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汁已经溢出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:19.92,1:05:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,, 很厉害呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:24.26,1:05:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你射之后还能再硬吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:27.60,1:05:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你是阿姨呀\N我好开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:31.60,1:05:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:44.11,1:05:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要自己来吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:47.62,1:05:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还是你来比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:53.96,1:05:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:58.13,1:05:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:01.80,1:06:03.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我随时可以射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:04.97,1:06:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:08.80,1:06:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被胸部夹住\N你马上要射了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:14.14,1:06:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要变得奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:16.65,1:06:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真二君的内棒   真是色情呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:20.65,1:06:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨\N你不用忍耐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:25.49,1:06:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好开心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:36.33,1:06:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:39.67,1:06:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多淫汁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:05.53,1:07:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:17.71,1:07:20.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真二君的表情   好色情
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:24.55,1:07:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都是因为阿姨啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:27.55,1:07:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为阿姨吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:32.05,1:07:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好开心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:37.89,1:07:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得这么精神了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:47.07,1:07:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要颤动吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:52.24,1:07:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样抚摸好爽快
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:56.58,1:07:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:09.09,1:08:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能变得这么大\N我好开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:13.09,1:08:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你是阿姨呀\N真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:18.60,1:08:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我最喜欢这个了\N最喜欢这个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:24.61,1:08:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以喔   我会尽情给你弄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:27.94,1:08:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？\N我会尽情给你弄
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:40.96,1:08:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唾液好爽快\N睡夜爽快是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:47.63,1:08:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好色情的声音\N又湿了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:57.14,1:08:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害\N被夹住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:59.64,1:09:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽快啊\N我帮你夹紧喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:07.15,1:09:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:11.65,1:09:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你用力的夹住
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:16.32,1:09:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太色情了\N变得色情了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:22.33,1:09:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太激烈的话   会不妙的\N不妙吗？   没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:27.34,1:09:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙就不妙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:45.02,1:09:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好色情呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:48.36,1:09:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着我呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:50.19,1:09:53.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的样子\N我会好好看着的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:54.36,1:09:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好看这你好色情的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:26.06,1:10:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:31.90,1:10:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太爽快了\N爽快是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:35.40,1:10:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒在颤动呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:01.76,1:11:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒好厉害    好硬阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:51.15,1:11:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨    我要射了\N可以呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:54.82,1:11:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行   要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:55.98,1:11:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:19.67,1:12:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又射了出来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:23.18,1:12:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又射了出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:45.53,1:12:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨   好痒阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:50.04,1:12:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痒是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:53.38,1:12:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你射了这么多出来\N我好开心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:17.73,1:13:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:09.74,1:16:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽快阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:16.91,1:16:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真二君
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:26.09,1:16:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:36.26,1:16:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太爽快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:19.64,1:17:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽快阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:37.99,1:17:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽快阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:44.67,1:17:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真二君   好爽快阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:55.84,1:17:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真二君
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:58.68,1:18:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真二君
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:14.03,1:18:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:16.70,1:18:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了  不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:19.70,1:18:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:23.37,1:18:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:25.87,1:18:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:31.55,1:18:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:36.38,1:18:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了   要去了   要去了\N不行  要去了  要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:46.90,1:18:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:13.48,1:20:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨你这身衣服是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:17.65,1:20:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:31.00,1:20:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没有给你送圣延节礼物吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:39.84,1:20:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聪在这个晚上跟女朋友第一次性爱\N肯定成为大人了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:50.19,1:20:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真二君你也不能输给他了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:54.86,1:20:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:03.70,1:21:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来给你一个最棒的圣诞节
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:11.04,1:21:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最棒的吗？\N没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:14.38,1:21:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你看好了\N好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:22.38,1:21:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:35.73,1:21:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边也舔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:45.07,1:21:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痒啊\N好痒是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:50.91,1:21:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为看不见\N所以更加敏感吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:02.76,1:22:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太厉害了\N可以听到淫荡的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:07.93,1:22:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以听到是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:16.94,1:22:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很让人兴奋是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:19.94,1:22:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很兴兴奋
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:24.11,1:22:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不可以偷看喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:31.79,1:22:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道你哪里爽快
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:55.98,1:22:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你大敏感了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:02.98,1:23:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你颤动这么厉害吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:09.16,1:23:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可爱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:16.50,1:23:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒已经这么硬\N对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:23.17,1:23:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用道歉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:31.01,1:23:35.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说过了吗？\N要送给你最棒的圣诞节
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:50.87,1:23:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好脏的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:53.70,1:23:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不脏呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:09.38,1:24:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乳头已经很挺立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:18.06,1:24:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要反抗呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:35.91,1:24:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会有感觉吗？因为看不到   所以非常有感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:41.75,1:24:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的肉棒很挺立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:02.60,1:25:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒好精神呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:20.29,1:25:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多淫汁溢出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:31.47,1:25:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:33.80,1:25:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在乱动
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:36.47,1:25:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我实在受不了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:44.48,1:25:49.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可爱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:09.50,1:26:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱的嘴巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:13.01,1:26:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要舔了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:28.42,1:27:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爽快吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:43.10,1:27:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痒啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:45.27,1:27:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痒是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:51.61,1:27:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有被人舔过  这种部位吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:57.11,1:27:59.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,i会有奇怪的感觉吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:02.78,1:28:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪的感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:08.12,1:28:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你起来呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:08.29,1:28:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给真二君做很多\N你没有做过的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:18.80,1:28:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你看不到   你也不知道\N我在干是吗吧   你在摸我的脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:27.81,1:28:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么嗯？你觉得我在干什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:18.53,1:29:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不臭吗？\N不臭呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:42.88,1:29:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的脚趾，我也给你舔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:48.39,1:29:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好淫荡呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:23.93,1:30:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样呢？\N会有奇怪的感觉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:28.43,1:30:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是好爽快
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:38.94,1:30:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:41.94,1:30:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个姿势好怪异喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:37.83,1:31:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊\N厉害是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:41.34,1:31:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你解开吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:46.68,1:31:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会尽情的给你舔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:50.01,1:31:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:05.19,1:32:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舌头进入屁眼眼了\N舌进入了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:24.71,1:32:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:42.40,1:32:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也没有想到   在这种奇怪的部位\N会如此爽快的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:46.40,1:32:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,性爱真的太厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:49.90,1:32:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:04.92,1:33:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢这个了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:08.76,1:33:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢乳头对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:13.43,1:33:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你的反应   我就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:33.28,1:33:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,颤动好厉害呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:47.63,1:33:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸了你的内棒之后\N我就兴奋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:53.47,1:33:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我摩擦呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:56.47,1:33:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能感觉到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:01.14,1:34:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你摩擦我的小穴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:26.00,1:34:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可爱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:34.34,1:34:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚肉棒跳动了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:41.52,1:34:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要保持这样喔\N还不能拿掉眼罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:48.02,1:34:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妤想干什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:55.20,1:34:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来阿   真二君喜欢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:06.04,1:35:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把舌头伸长呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:11.21,1:35:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:14.88,1:35:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:17.05,1:35:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:26.23,1:35:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽快阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:54.42,1:35:58.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真二君你都没有看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:59.43,1:36:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是你的舌头却伸进去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:03.43,1:36:07.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不见\N看不见     舌头也进去了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:21.12,1:36:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真二君我会爽快的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:30.29,1:36:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样啪啦啪啦的舔\N我会去的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:41.97,1:36:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了\N真二君
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:45.97,1:36:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太厉害了\N小穴好爽快阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:48.48,1:36:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真二君   好厉害阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:53.32,1:36:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽快阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:59.32,1:37:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害阿  我要去了\N不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:03.16,1:37:08.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害阿   不行了  真二君\N我要去了   要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:10.67,1:37:12.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:30.19,1:37:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真二君\N我无法忍耐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:38.36,1:37:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:40.03,1:37:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗？\N你知道现在碰触哪里吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:46.53,1:37:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道   是淫荡的部位吧\N你知道碰触到淫荡的部位了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:53.38,1:37:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看阿    我要插入了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:58.55,1:37:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:02.55,1:38:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真二君进去了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:13.56,1:38:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真二君
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:19.07,1:38:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面好爽快呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:23.41,1:38:25.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变大了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:33.75,1:38:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大肉棒\N我最喜欢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:41.92,1:38:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我嘴喜欢阿姨的小穴了\N真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:58.44,1:39:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽快阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:20.80,1:39:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真二君的肉棒\N我想一直插入
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:31.81,1:39:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为看不到  我很兴奋\N很兴奋是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:36.48,1:39:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我一边 揉弄这里\N一边插入吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:40.32,1:39:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我会射的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:42.65,1:39:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会射吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:59.33,1:40:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很爽快吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:02.17,1:40:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以集中在肉棒上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:06.68,1:40:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你这样说
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:09.18,1:40:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道要怎么做\N你集中在肉棒上呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:14.35,1:40:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真二君的肉棒不断在小穴里面抽动呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:30.87,1:40:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害    插入很深呢\N真二君
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:39.21,1:40:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒爽快吗？\N好爽快
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:43.04,1:40:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒爽快是吗\N是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:51.55,1:40:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穴也很爽快呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:01.23,1:41:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒在颤动呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:12.24,1:41:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太爽快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:14.08,1:41:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?真二君你的腰在抽动呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:21.58,1:41:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在抽动呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:24.92,1:41:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不行的肉棒呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:27.92,1:41:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此的肉棒   真是抱歉呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:31.26,1:41:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:36.60,1:41:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:39.60,1:41:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:42.60,1:41:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在抽动吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:45.44,1:41:47.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会去的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:48.61,1:41:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:50.61,1:41:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒不行阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:53.28,1:41:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行要去了   要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:04.63,1:42:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你在抽动啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:08.30,1:42:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为在阿姨的里面抽动\N太爽快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:12.80,1:42:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒这么爽快吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:34.32,1:42:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真二君你知道怎变样了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:51.17,1:42:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真二君的肉棒太粗了\N所以里面很爽快喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:05.52,1:43:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:08.86,1:43:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真二君     插入到里面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:19.03,1:43:20.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是受不了阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:23.54,1:43:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:41.39,1:43:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要继续了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:47.23,1:43:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会尽情抽动的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:56.57,1:43:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害，这个很爽快
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:00.91,1:44:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真二君
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:20.60,1:44:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不行了   真二君
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:24.27,1:44:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨想要更加爽快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:36.28,1:44:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要帮我解开吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:47.79,1:44:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美味吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:03.97,1:45:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想要\N还想要是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:06.64,1:45:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从后面抽动呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:13.65,1:45:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从后面来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:17.15,1:45:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你抽动阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:41.01,1:45:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:51.69,1:45:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要握住我的腰吗?真二君
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:55.69,1:45:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你握住我的腰\N这样会插入很深的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:00.36,1:46:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部插入了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:02.70,1:46:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面   插入好深阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:07.70,1:46:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:10.71,1:46:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的   不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:15.71,1:46:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行    真二君   不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:20.55,1:46:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了   不行的   要去了\N要去了   不行   要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:40.07,1:46:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够看到比较好\N看到比较好是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:56.92,1:46:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好色情呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:58.92,1:47:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太色情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:06.60,1:47:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行   好爽快阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:08.93,1:47:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:18.94,1:47:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:20.61,1:47:23.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害\N要去了 要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:40.46,1:47:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:50.81,1:47:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行   要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:00.48,1:48:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你发出这么可爱的声音\N我会射的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:05.49,1:48:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会射吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:08.49,1:48:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不可以吧？\N还不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:22.67,1:48:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要进去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:25.51,1:48:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插入了   真二君的肉棒\N好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:31.85,1:48:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插入的部位    都看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:43.02,1:48:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害阿    讨厌啦\N不要抽出来呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:48.53,1:48:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:51.53,1:48:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要抽出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:06.21,1:49:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:18.39,1:49:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穴在颤动呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:21.06,1:49:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穴要收缩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:36.41,1:49:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的样子好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:48.92,1:49:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:52.43,1:49:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行   不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:57.43,1:50:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行   真二君\N不行    我真的要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:03.94,1:50:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:07.11,1:50:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接吻呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:13.78,1:50:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么靠近的话   我会射的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:17.45,1:50:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要射了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:29.13,1:50:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:32.13,1:50:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽快阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:36.64,1:50:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒  里面\N要去了  要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:05.67,1:51:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真二君
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:09.17,1:51:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫我步美呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:12.84,1:51:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了   不是阿姨吗了\N我想你叫我步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:20.18,1:51:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗？\N你叫我的名字呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:29.52,1:51:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步美   真二君
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:36.53,1:51:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真二君   步美\N好厉害阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:41.20,1:51:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽快阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:50.71,1:51:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽快阿   那里面    好爽快阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:56.05,1:51:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行   要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:01.06,1:52:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:04.56,1:52:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行   要去了   不行\N要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:11.07,1:52:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:12.57,1:52:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了\N去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:21.41,1:52:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:29.42,1:52:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你继续喊我的名字呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:39.59,1:52:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:41.10,1:52:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:49.44,1:52:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:56.44,1:52:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:58.11,1:52:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法忍耐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:07.12,1:53:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步美你爽快吗?\N爽快   好爽快   好厉害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:13.13,1:53:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超爽快的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:20.97,1:53:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行   不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:31.65,1:53:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在颤动呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:35.32,1:53:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大厉害了\N好爽快
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:41.99,1:53:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步美我想射了\N你想射了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:47.50,1:53:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的    射到你想射的部位吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:51.33,1:53:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的\N可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:55.34,1:53:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想射到步美的睑上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:58.34,1:54:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以喔    你射吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:01.51,1:54:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以射吗？\N可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:06.01,1:54:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射出来阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:29.37,1:54:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:09.91,1:55:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射了很多出来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:13.25,1:55:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害   真二君的精液把我弄脏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:34.77,1:55:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射了很多出来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:08.47,1:56:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不能相信    你就相信吧\N是骗人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:12.64,1:56:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样太奇怪了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:15.31,1:56:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧     绝对没有啦\N真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:19.31,1:56:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聪你回来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:22.48,1:56:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?\N早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:26.49,1:56:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸不在家   你睡得真晚呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:29.66,1:56:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉    我马上去弄早餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:34.50,1:56:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了   那简直是最糟糕的圣诞节了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:39.33,1:56:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟女朋友什么都没有发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:43.67,1:56:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为总算可以处男毕业了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:47.18,1:56:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说让我集中精神学习吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:51.35,1:56:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？   不过对我来说\N你这个处男是没有办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:57.85,1:57:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙    要迟到了\N妈妈    不用弄早餐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:03.02,1:57:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了\N打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:10.20,1:57:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出门了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:30.39,1:57:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步美谢谢你送我一个很棒的圣诞节
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:41.90,1:57:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错    丈夫以外   我第一个爱上的男人\N就是我儿子的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:50.07,1:57:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是发生在圣诞节的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:53.58,1:57:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这肯定是圣诞老人送给我的礼物
